 SEVENTEEN 的 Seungkwan 写下支持韩国流行偶像的信息https://www.nme.com/news/music/seventeen-seungkwan-pens-message-supporting-fellow-k-​​pop-idols-3807323?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=seventeen-seungkwan-pens-message-supporting-韩国流行偶像Gladys YeoTue, 29 Oct 2024 05:54:26 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3807323 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="十七胜官" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我不想再看到人们互相伤害”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/seventeen-seungkwan-pens-message-supporting-fellow-k-pop-idols-3807323">SEVENTEEN 的 Seungkwan 所写的关于支持韩国流行偶像的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="十七胜官" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/seventeen-seungkwan-291024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/seventeen">SEVENTEEN</a>歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/seungkwan">Seungkwan</a>在 Instagram 上发布了一条有关韩国流行音乐行业的长文，并表达了他对其他偶像的支持。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/mamamoo-hwasa-interview-o-new-lease-on-life-3803967">华莎谈寻找新的生活：“我只是按照我内心的愿望前进”</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周，韩国流行音乐公司<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hybe">HYBE</a>在国会文化、体育和旅游委员会审计期间披露了公司文件。此后，数页<a href="https://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20241025050524" target="_blank" rel="noopener">据称包含对韩国流行音乐艺术家的贬低言论</a>的文件被泄露，引发了国内外韩国流行音乐粉丝的愤怒。</p><p>在持续不断的争议中，SEVENTEEN 歌手 Seungkwan 分享了一条为他的乐队和其他韩国流行偶像说话的信息。 “我不想再看到人们互相伤害，”他在<a href="https://www.soompi.com/article/1699048wpp/seventeens-seungkwan-personally-speaks-up-in-light-of-recent-situation-involving-hybe" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Soompi</em></a>上写道。 “我觉得我不能再为此刻仍在努力工作的所有同事、我的粉丝、我的成员、我受伤的人们保持沉默。” </p><figure id="attachment_3608417" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3608417" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3608417" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Seungkwan-of-SEVENTEEN-performs-live.jpg" alt="SEVENTEEN 胜宽现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Seungkwan-of-SEVENTEEN-performs-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Seungkwan-of-SEVENTEEN-performs-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Seungkwan-of-SEVENTEEN-performs-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Seungkwan-of-SEVENTEEN-performs-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Seungkwan-of-SEVENTEEN-performs-live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Seungkwan-of-SEVENTEEN-performs-live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3608417" class="wp-caption-text"> SEVENTEEN 的 Seungkwan 将于 2022 年 12 月 10 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶的洛杉矶州立历史公园举办 2022 LA3C 音乐节。图片来源：莎拉·莫里斯/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>这位歌手写道，虽然作为名人有一些事情需要忍受，但他不认为“这是一份我们必须忍受到自我毁灭、受伤直到死亡边缘的工作。”</p><p> “我们经历了足够多的痛苦，崩溃了，并以某种方式克服了它，付出了顽强的努力，在舞台上为我们的粉丝展示我们最好的一面，”他谈到 SEVENTEEN 和韩国流行音乐界的同行时说道。 “我希望人们不要轻视偶像。”</p><p> “你没有权利轻易介入我们的叙述。不只是我们，还有其他艺术家，我们不是你的物品。我希望你不要认为你可以随心所欲地使用和享受我们，”Seungkwan 继续说道。</p><p>他接着对与其他韩国流行偶像的鼓励和互动表示感谢，并补充说这些给了他力量。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBrWmlSS39F/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554