swift@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kid-rock">Kid Rock</a>谈到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eminem">阿姆</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡玛拉·哈里斯</a>竞选美国总统 - 看看这位说唱歌手在下面怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/eminem-the-death-of-slim-shady-coup-de-grace-album-review-3774875">埃米纳姆 – 《The Death of Slim Shady (Coup De Grâce)》评论：精心制作的歌曲和空洞的挑衅</a></strong></li></ul><p>九月，泰勒·斯威夫特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-endorsement-of-kamala-harris-for-president-3792514">宣布支持卡玛拉·哈里斯</a>。埃米纳姆上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/obama-raps-lose-yourself-verse-at-kamala-harris-rally-after-being-introduced-by-eminem-3805325">出席哈里斯底特律集会并介绍了前总统巴拉克·奥巴马</a>时证实了他的支持。 </p><figure id="attachment_3807298" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3807298" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3807298" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3807298" class="wp-caption-text">巴拉克·奥巴马和埃米纳姆在卡马拉·哈里斯的底特律集会上。图片来源：DOMINIC GWINN/中东图片/法新社盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>Kid Rock 长期以来一直是<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>的支持者，可以追溯到 2016 年这位前总统的选举。近几个月来，Kid Rock（真名罗伯特“鲍勃”里奇）已经成为特朗普阵营的代言人，并出现在多个场合集会支持共和党候选人。</p><p>自从阿姆出现在哈里斯的集会上后，摇滚小子就在社交媒体上表达了他对阿姆和泰勒·斯威夫特对哈里斯支持的看法。在发布到 X 的一段视频中，可以看到这位乡村说唱歌手赤裸上身弹奏着原声吉他。他停下来说道：“现在我引起了你们的注意，我爱阿姆。我们已经是很多年的朋友了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3807299" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3807299" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3807299" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3807299" class="wp-caption-text"> 2018 年唐纳德·特朗普和 Kid Rock。图片来源：SAUL LOEB/AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Kid Rock 继续说道：“我不同意他的政治观点，但我确实赞扬他和像泰勒·斯威夫特这样的人站出来，并且不害怕为他们所相信的事情发声。以不同的方式思考并拥有这样做的自由才是这个国家的伟大之处。”</p><p>随后，他加大了对特朗普的支持，并补充道：“我的立场是明确的，让美国再次伟大，因为我内心、思想、身体和灵魂都知道，特朗普总统将使美国再次伟大。上帝保佑美国。”</p><blockquote class