jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-payne">利亚姆·佩恩</a>的第一首遗作歌曲将于本周晚些时候发行——了解更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755">Liam Payne 1993-2024：单向明星帮助引发了流行现象</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位独唱艺术家和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>成员于 10 月 16 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">从阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯卡萨苏尔巴勒莫酒店三楼阳台坠落</a>身亡。阿根廷检察官办公室透露，这名31岁的男子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-cause-of-death-and-details-of-hotel-room-in-disarray-revealed-3803859">的死因是多处外伤和内外出血</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3806079" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3806079" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3806079" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3806079" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩.图片来源：Hanna Lassen/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>现在，格莱美奖制作人兼歌手萨姆·庞兹（Sam Pounds）在社交媒体上宣布即将发行一首他们共同制作的歌曲，在佩恩不幸去世之前，他一直与佩恩一起在录音室里。</p><p>庞兹写道：“我祈祷这将成为利亚姆一直梦想的世界的祝福。我祈祷天使每天都会在聆听时安慰你们。我祈祷这首歌能够祝福露丝、贝尔和整个家庭。我祈祷这首歌能够消除负面的回响。我祈祷超自然的积极治愈力量将拥抱你们每一个人……带着爱，让我们都成为祝福。”</p><p> Pounds 分享的一张名为“Do No Wrong”的歌曲封面图片包括 11 月 1 日的发行日期。这首歌将以三种形式提供：原版、现场混音版和无伴奏合唱版。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">萨姆·庞兹<a href="https://t.co/wWn3SNOs9t">https://t.co/wWn3SNOs9t</a></p><p>我祈祷这将成为利亚姆一直梦想的世界的祝福。我祈祷天使每天都会在聆听时安慰你们。我祈祷这首歌能够祝福露丝、贝尔和整个家庭。我祈祷这首歌...... <a href="https://t.co/nX0e9qcNon">pic.twitter.com/nX0e9qcNon</a></p><p> — Sam Pounds (@iamsampounds) <a href="https://twitter.com/iamsampounds/status/1850960328428867815?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 10 月 28 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>当佩恩去世的消息传出时，萨姆·庞兹在社交媒体上向他已故的合作者致敬，分享了他们一起出去玩的几段视频，佩恩还为这首歌录制了他的声音。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBO4D46Rebe/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000